                <img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width:180px;height:auto;display:block;margin:-40px 0 10px 0;">
<div class="pillar-label">Module 1</div>
                <div class="chapter-label">Chapter 2</div>
                <h1>Three Initial AI Decisions That Will Set Your Course</h1>
                
                <p class="intro-text">AI can be transformative, but only when it serves your strategy, not the other way around. The choices your leadership team make at the beginning of your AI journey will determine how effectively AI strengthens your operations, improves your customers' experiences, and drives sustainable growth for years.</p>
                
                <p class="chapter-description">This chapter helps you make three early decisions that will shape how fast, and how safely, you adopt AI across your business.</p>
            </div>
